definition: according to/in accordance with/to shine/to illuminate/to reflect/to look at (one's reflection)/to take (a photo)/photo/as requested/as before

sentences.english: I only brought my passport and the Foreign Employment License.
sentences.chinese: 我只帶了護照和外國人就業證。

sentences.english: Hello. This is the Yanhua Fenghuang Hospital. May I see your passport please.
sentences.chinese: 您好，這裏是燕化鳳凰醫院，請出示您的護照。

sentences.english: May I see your passport and customs declaration form?
sentences.chinese: 可以看你的護照和報關單嗎？

sentences.english: Australian reports said the other three men were Chinese passport-holders.
sentences.chinese: 澳大利亞稱其他三名男子持中國護照。

sentences.english: May I have your passport and arrival card, please?
sentences.chinese: 請出示您的護照和入境卡？

sentences.english: Attach one passport-size photograph of yourself in the space provided.
sentences.chinese: 將自己的護照大小的照片中所提供的空間。

sentences.english: He opened the bag and found some dollars and a passport in it.
sentences.chinese: 他打開提包發現裏面有一些美元和一份護照。

sentences.english: Six light-minded girls are losing their passports and money on their way to Ibiza.
sentences.chinese: 六個頭腦簡單的女孩在去伊比薩的路上丟了護照和錢。

sentences.english: Yes, Passport and the disembarkation card, please.
sentences.chinese: 是的，請給我護照，以及旅客入境登記表。

sentences.english: My passport is out of date.
EMMA NORTHEY: "The children were each given a passport."
sentences.chinese: 每個孩子都發了一個護照。

sentences.english: Please show me your passport and your health certificate.
sentences.chinese: 請出示您的護照和健康證。

sentences.english: Your group members' passports and two one-by-one inch photos, pls.
sentences.chinese: 請給我你們組員的護照和寸照兩張。

sentences.english: You can use your private passport for your graduation.
sentences.chinese: 你可以使用你的因私護照。

sentences.english: Virtual passports are stamped at each national pavilion.
sentences.chinese: 每個展館都會幫你在虛擬護照上蓋章。

sentences.english: Please write down your name, nationality, and passport number on this registration card.
sentences.chinese: 請把你的姓名，國籍，和護照號寫在這張登記卡上。
